OL,3,CSunak's former aide among 15 charged
OL,4,Cwith gambling offences over election
OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FRishi Sunak's former aide Craig
OL,8,FWilliams and 14 others have been
OL,9,Fcharged with gambling offences
OL,10,Ffollowing an investigation into bets
OL,11,Fplaced on the timing of the 2024
OL,12,Felection.
OL,14,FWilliams, a former Tory MP, was among
OL,15,Fa number of people linked to the
OL,16,FConservative Party reported to have
OL,17,Fmade bets on the election date, which
OL,18,Fwas called by then-prime minister
OL,19,FRishi Sunak.
