OL,7,FLaura Saunders, who was Tory candidate
OL,8,Ffor Bristol North West at the election
OL,9,Fand is married to the party's campaign
OL,10,Fchief, has also been charged with the
OL,11,Fsame offence.
OL,13,FThe investigation, which was started
OL,14,Fin June 2024, looked at specific
OL,15,Findividuals using confidential
OL,16,Finformation, specifically advanced
OL,17,Fknowledge of the proposed election
OL,18,Fdate, to gain an unfair advantage in
OL,19,Fthe betting markets.
