OL,7,FThose charged with a criminal offence
OL,8,Funder Section 42 of the Gambling Act
OL,9,F2005 are:
OL,11,FThey are due to appear at Westminster
OL,12,FMagistrates Court at 10am on Friday
OL,13,FJune 13, 2025.
OL,15,FAmong others facing charges are
OL,16,FRussell George, the Senedd member for
OL,17,FMontgomeryshire, and Nick Mason, a
OL,18,Fformer chief data officer for the
OL,19,FConservative Party.
