OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FThe former Montgomeryshire MP admitted
OL,8,Fat the time to having a "flutter" on
OL,9,Fthe election date just days before it
OL,10,Fwas announced in May last year.
OL,12,FDarren Millar, the leader of the Welsh
OL,13,FConservatives, said: "Having been
OL,14,Finformed that Russell George MS has
OL,15,Fbeen charged with gambling-related
OL,16,Foffences, I have taken the decision to
OL,17,Fsuspend him from the Welsh
OL,18,FConservative group in the Senedd.
