OL,7,F"The suspension is a neutral act
OL,8,Fpending the outcome of the justice
OL,9,Fprocess.
OL,11,F"There will be no further comment at
OL,12,Fthis time."
OL,14,FA Tory Party spokesman said: "The
OL,15,FConservative Party believes that those
OL,16,Fworking in politics must act with
OL,17,Fintegrity.
OL,19,F"Current members of staff who have
OL,20,Fbeen charged are being suspended with
OL,21,Fimmediate effect.
