OL,7,F"These incidents took place in May
OL,8,Flast year. Our party is now under new
OL,9,Fleadership and we are co-operating
OL,10,Ffully with the Gambling Commission to
OL,11,Fensure that their investigation can
OL,12,Fconclude swiftly and transparently."
OL,14,FLabour Party chairwoman Ellie Reeves
OL,15,Fsaid: "Kemi Badenoch must make crystal
OL,16,Fclear that anyone found guilty of
OL,17,Fusing insider information to cheat the
OL,18,Fsystem to try to enrich themselves has
OL,19,Fno place in the Conservative Party. No
OL,20,Fifs, no buts.
